    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 本款游戏</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0da8cfb490b046cf14d7c429a2811c5b.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0da8cfb490b046cf14d7c429a2811c5b.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0da8cfb490b046cf14d7c429a2811c5b.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>战争迷雾</strong>能够隐藏敌方军队。因此<strong>《后翼弃兵：迷雾棋局》</strong>既考验你快速决策、战术思考和敢于冒险的能力，也需要你在踏入黑雾探查未知之前进行细致考量。游戏规则经过强化与改进后，将给忠实的国际象棋爱好者和休闲玩家带来无穷的乐趣。游戏中的意外事件和无法预料的攻击将总会让玩家兴奋不已。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/b2eb05251a5d13635ba99c6f2820f411.avif?t=1754999139\" width=610 height=239 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 颠覆性的战争迷雾系统<br></li><li>完整的、叙述式的、由故事主导的战役模式<br></li><li>遭遇并挑战著名的国王与皇后<br></li><li>全新的国际象棋视觉体验<br></li><li>可自定义的头像和个人资料<br></li><li>PvP和变种国际象棋模式 </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >冒险时间</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/4876344926f3c9625ac6032c6743fcb7.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/4876344926f3c9625ac6032c6743fcb7.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/4876344926f3c9625ac6032c6743fcb7.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>迈开脚步，深入《后翼弃兵：迷雾棋局》的单人战役模式，与过去的皇后与国王作战。 <br>你敢于挑战著名的<strong>成吉思汗</strong>、智取<strong>所罗门王</strong>或是战胜<strong>伊凡大帝</strong>吗? 敢于和<strong>伊丽莎白女王</strong>或<strong>慈禧太后</strong>辩驳，并始终保持头脑清醒吗？但请小心，他们中的一些人可不会按规则行事！ <br><br>下完第一步后，开动脑筋，随时准备好应对意外事件。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/edc3d4d358ac4a2e24d7043606788e58.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/edc3d4d358ac4a2e24d7043606788e58.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/edc3d4d358ac4a2e24d7043606788e58.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PvP模式</h2><br>通关了战役并解决了所有的谜题？这还不是《后翼弃兵：迷雾棋局》的所有内容！现在你已经准备好迎接更大的挑战了！你可以在PvP模式中和其他玩家对战，聪明狡猾可不是你一个人的特权！在特别排位赛中达到最高等级即可解锁<strong>迷雾棋局大师</strong>的称号。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/a009008efc40fef620525d10f82ac2be.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/a009008efc40fef620525d10f82ac2be.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/a009008efc40fef620525d10f82ac2be.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > 奖励与自定义</h2><br>你是否曾在赢得一场艰难的国际象棋对决后，希望自己的努力能够得到一些奖励，却无法如愿以偿？<strong>《后翼弃兵：迷雾棋局》</strong>将对你获得的成就进行奖励！对于你解决的每个谜题、战胜的每个对手或是机智的每一步棋，你都会获得一个成就并解锁新的视觉内容作为奖励。你可以自定义游戏中的头像。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0bb5202fe3d7e58b96a2b5f180d8600e.poster.avif?t=1754999139\" width=620 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0bb5202fe3d7e58b96a2b5f180d8600e.webm?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1151130/extras/0bb5202fe3d7e58b96a2b5f180d8600e.mp4?t=1754999139\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>无论你是忠实的国际象棋爱好者还是桌面游戏爱好者，《后翼弃兵：迷雾棋局》欢迎所有玩家享受国际象棋对战的快乐。",
